sec.p:
For an absorption process involving p photons, the intensity of the PL, IPL, is proportional to the excitation intensity to the power of p, (Iexc)p\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
